<post author="tara1223" datetime="2012-02-02T07:29:00" id="p3">
I love, love Charleston!
What about Savannah?
My family always went to Jekyll Island in Georgia (DH and I try to go every few years now). Its got beaches, and parks, and a sea turtle hospital. Its about an hour from Florida, 45 mins to Savannah...its one of my favorite places.

Or Disney!
</post>
