<post author="Falada45" datetime="2012-03-27T12:08:00" id="p3">
Maybe consider Eureka Springs, AR?
It's about 4 hours from KC. Has lots of cute shops and art galleries and festivals from time to time. They also have a really cool wildlife reserve called Turpentine Creek with some big cats (tigers, lions, etc.) and bears that have been rescued from auctions/abusive situations.
